---
title: Turmeric-Spiced Pea & Leek Fritters with Lemony Asparagus Almondine
description: Both mild and sweet, peas and leeks are a natural flavor combo. These turmeric-spiced fritters are the best of both worlds—creamy on the inside and crispy on the outside. A side of lemon zest-spiked asparagus, topped with crunchy almonds, is the
perfect Spring side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5556133bf8b25e921f8b456a.
